                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310217-120-victim1252 t18310217-120-viclabel714"></join>. On the 7th of February, about eight o'clock, I was in his shop - the prisoner and this piece of flannel were brought in by two young men; the flannel has our mark on it, and the mark of the person we bought it of - I had seen it safe half an hour before, laying on three other pieces in the shop; we sent for an officer.</p>
